'''自閉症人權運動'''（{{lang-en|Autism rights movement}}，別名：自閉症文化運動、神經多樣性運動）是在殘疾人權利背景下強調{{Tsl|en|neurodiversity paradigm|神經多樣性範式}}的一個[[社會運動|社會運動]]，支持者認爲[[自閉症譜系障礙|自閉症譜系障礙]]是[[人腦|人類大腦]]自然的變化，而非一種疾病。<ref name="Solomon">{{Cite news|work=New York|title=The autism rights movement|author=Solomon|first=Andrew|date=2008-05-25|accessdate=2008-05-27|url=https://nymag.com/news/features/47225/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080527025140/http://nymag.com/news/features/47225/|archivedate=27 May 2008}}</ref> 該運動主張有幾個目標，比如要求更大程度對自閉症行爲的接受；將重點放在改善生活質量而非模仿[[神经学典范|神经学典范]]同伴上<ref name="Bigthink">{{Cite web|title=Should Autism Be Cured or Is "Curing" Offensive?|url=https://bigthink.com/paul-ratner/should-autism-be-cured-or-is-curing-offfensive|accessdate=16 June 2019|author=Ratner|date=10 July 2016|first=Paul|work=Big Think|language=en|archive-date=2019-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616072634/https://bigthink.com/paul-ratner/should-autism-be-cured-or-is-curing-offfensive|dead-url=no}}</ref>；以及將自閉症群體看作[[少数群体|少數群體]]<ref name="Jaarsma2012">{{Cite journal|title=Autism as a natural human variation: reflections on the claims of the neurodiversity movement|url=http://urn.kb.se/resolve?urn=urn:nbn:se:liu:diva-72172|last=Jaarsma|first=Pier|last2=Welin|first2=Stellan|date=2012|journal=Health Care Analysis: HCA: Journal of Health Philosophy and Policy|issue=1|doi=10.1007/s10728-011-0169-9|volume=20|pages=20–30|issn=1573-3394|pmid=21311979|access-date=2020-08-30|archive-date=2019-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191217074222/http://liu.diva-portal.org/smash/record.jsf?pid=diva2%3A457919&dswid=-943|dead-url=no}}</ref>

自閉症權利與神經多樣性主張[[自閉症光譜|自閉症譜系]]應被看作[[人類基因組|人類基因組]]的自然表達，應在社會上與其他社會狀態相同對待（障礙者社會模式）。但在醫療角度上看，自閉症是基因缺陷，且應該通過追蹤自閉症基因的方式來進行處理。一種非主流邊緣理論則認爲自閉症是由於環境因素所導致，<ref name="Jaarsma2012">{{Cite journal|title=Autism as a natural human variation: reflections on the claims of the neurodiversity movement|url=http://urn.kb.se/resolve?urn=urn:nbn:se:liu:diva-72172|last=Jaarsma|first=Pier|last2=Welin|first2=Stellan|date=2012|journal=Health Care Analysis: HCA: Journal of Health Philosophy and Policy|issue=1|doi=10.1007/s10728-011-0169-9|volume=20|pages=20–30|issn=1573-3394|pmid=21311979}}</ref> 比如疫苗。<ref name="Solomon">{{Cite news|work=New York|title=The autism rights movement|author=Solomon|first=Andrew|date=2008-05-25|accessdate=2008-05-27|url=https://nymag.com/news/features/47225/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080527025140/http://nymag.com/news/features/47225/|archivedate=27 May 2008}}</ref>

